    <div class="block__content">
      <p><strong>Please note that we do not run any frontline services. Please check for suitable organisations in the <a href="/find-help/">Find Help</a> section if you are experiencing homelessness and need support.</strong></p>

      <h2 class="h2">Charities and Voluntary Groups</h2>
      <p>If you are a Manchester or Leeds based organisation, and would like your services to be listed, you can <a href="/register/">register</a> through the site. If you would like any information to be changed or removed, and you do not have a login, please let us know at <a href="mailto:admin@streetsupport.net">admin@streetsupport.net</a>.</p>

      <h2 class="h2">Corporate Partners</h2>
      <p>If you are a business that share our values and would like to support our mission, please contact <a href="mailto:sponsorship@streetsupport.net">sponsorship@streetsupport.net</a>.</p>

      <h2 class="h2">General Questions</h2>
      <p>If you have any questions, ideas, or would like to know more about us, you can get in touch at <a href="mailto:info@streetsupport.net">info@streetsupport.net</a>.</p>

      <h2 class="h2">General Updates</h2>
      <p>You can join the conversation on <a href="https://twitter.com/streetsupportuk">Twitter</a>, <a href="https://www.facebook.com/streetsupport/">Facebook</a> or subscribe to <a href="http://streetsupport.us12.list-manage1.com/subscribe?u=da9a1d4bb2b1a69a981456972&id=52ba96f2af">our mailing list</a>.</p>

      <h2 class="h2">In person</h2>
      <p>You are welcome to come and visit us in person at Neo, Charlotte Street, Manchester, M1 4ET. We are often out visiting organisations so please contact us first by emailing <a href="mailto:info@streetsupport.net">info@streetsupport.net</a>, or you can contact Gary by phone on 07824 667709.</p>

